<section sectnbr = "5B">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A5206014" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Rastavljanje i sastavljanje petog stupnja prijenosa
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206010">Demontaža i montaža jedinice ručnog mjenjača</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5206013">Komponente sklopa ručnog mjenjača</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5206014001">
<title>
Rastavljanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite sklop poluge mjenjača i vratila birača. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5206012"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite vijke bočnog poklopca i skinite bočni poklopac mjenjača (1) koristeći posebni alat.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Obavezno pazite da ne deformirate bočni poklopac kada je uklonjen s lijevog kućišta mjenjača.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B004">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09921-96510">
09921-96510
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure page = "2">
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A522015.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "80.796mm" ver = "01" gw = "216" gh = "213"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Kliještima za uskočnike, uklonite rascjepku (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite vijak vilice 5. stupnja prijenosa (2).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Zajedno uklonite vilicu 5. stupnja prijenosa (3) i zupčanik 5. stupnja. Koristite izvlakač zupčanika za uklanjanje ako je spoj tijela čvrst.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RH01520015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.320mm" ver = "01" gw = "184" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Oslobodite maticu predložnog vratila (2), ugradite ulazno vratilo 5. stupnja (1) i specijalni alat da biste zaustavili rotiranje vratila, i zatim uklonite maticu predložnog vratila (2).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B005">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09927-76060">
09927-76060
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RH01520016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.307mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite ulazno vratilo 5. stupnja, igličasti ležaj i zatim zupčanik 5. stupnja predložnog vratila (1). Izvlakač zupčanika (2) će biti potreban ako je spoj sa žlijebom zupčanika 5. stupnja predložnog vratila čvrst.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A522016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.631mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "121"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5206014002">
<title>
Ponovno sastavljanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite 5. stupanj prijenosa predložnog vratila na (1) na predložno vratilo kao što je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.995mm" ver = "01" gw = "137" gh = "120"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.370in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.370in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
 Strana predložnog vratila
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[c]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
 Kratka prirubnica (Vanjska)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[b]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
 Duga prirubnica (Unutarnja)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nanesite ulje mjenjača na igličasti ležaj (3) i ugradite ga na ulazno vratilo.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite zupčanik 5. stupnja ulaznog vratila (1) na ulazno vratilo.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite specijalni alat kako biste spriječili rotiranje vratila.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B006">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09927-76060">
09927-76060
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pritegnite maticu predložnog vratila (2) propisanim momentom pritezanja i maticu osigurajte.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Pazite da upotrijebite novu maticu predložnog vratila.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Pazite da ne slomite brtvilo matice (4) predložnog vratila dok brtvite. Ako se slomi, zamijenite novim.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5B010">
<t-part>
Matica predložnog vratila
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
100
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
10,2
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
74,0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "76.485mm" ver = "01" gw = "206" gh = "200"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Sastavite ogrlicu sinkrona 5. stupnja (1), tijelo sinkrona 5. stupnja (2), poluge sinkrona 5. stupnja (3) i prsten sinkrona 5. stupnja (4) kako slijedi.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RH01520054.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "58.366mm" ver = "01" gw = "164" gh = "148"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Ugradite tijelo sinkrona 5. stupnja (1) na ogrlicu sinkrona 5. stupnja (2) u označenom smjeru kao što je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "40.722mm" ver = "02" gw = "199" gh = "99"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.056in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.188in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Skošena strana
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[b]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Dugačko izbočenje
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Podesite poluge sinkrona 5. stupnja prijenosa (1) na tijelo sinkrona 5. stupnja prijenosa (2) tako da poravnate izdanak (3) poluga sinkrona 5. stupnja (1) s utorom tijela čine sinkrona 5. stupnja prijenosa (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A522047.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.997mm" ver = "01" gw = "125" gh = "117"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Ugradite prsten sinkrona 5. stupnja (1) na tijelo sinkrona 5. stupnja (2) u oodređenom smjeru kao što je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I4RH01520055.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.169mm" ver = "01" gw = "83" gh = "118"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite vilicu odabira 5. stupnja (1) na sklop ogrlice sinkrona 5. stupnja (3) i tijela sinkrona 5. stupnja prijenosa (2), a zatim ih ugradite na ulazno vratilo i vratilo mjenjača poravnavajući utisnutu oznaku (4) s odgovarajućom oznakom (5) na ulaznom vratilu.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A520080.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "105.991mm" ver = "01" gw = "170" gh = "283"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Zategnite vijak vilice odabira 5. stupnja prijenosa (2) propisanim momentom pritezanja.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Obavezno primijenite novi vijak vilice odabira 5. stupnja prijenosa (2) obložen ljepilom. U suprotnom, vijci se mogu olabaviti.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5B011">
<t-part>
Vijak vilice odabira 5. stupnja prijenosa
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
10
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
1,0
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
7,5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Kliještima za uskočnike ugradite novu rascjepku (1) na ulazno vratilo (3) u određenom smjeru prema prikazu na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A522050.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.339mm" ver = "02" gw = "232" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
